headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Ocelot Jugular
content: Presenting the hot-blooded, cool-headed Ocelot Jugular. A model sportscar, this baby can cut down the road with the precision of a surgeon, if that surgeon could deliver 1,269 kilonewtons doing nothing more than dropping a deuce, and backhand a man with a slap-mass of 129.4 metric tons.
